STATE of North Carolina
v.
Kenneth KING. No. 613P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2007. Bruce T. Cunningham, Jr., Southern Pines, for King. John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 4th day of December 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of May 2007."
